{
  "video_id": "Uq3MCf_6HtI",
  "title": "How I became part sea urchin | Catherine Mohr",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12906.0,
      "end_time": 15985.0,
      "text": "My story starts in the northern Galapagos Islands,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16100.000000000002,
      "end_time": 19414.0,
      "text": "under 50 feet of water and a big school of sharks."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20148.0,
      "end_time": 23119.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d been scuba diving with a group of friends for about a week,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23143.0,
      "end_time": 24472.0,
      "text": "and it had been glorious:"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24496.0,
      "end_time": 27124.0,
      "text": "manta rays, whale sharks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27148.0,
      "end_time": 29898.0,
      "text": "penguins and, of course, hammerhead sharks."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30675.0,
      "end_time": 34770.0,
      "text": "Today&#39;s dive was particularly tricky."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34101.0,
      "end_time": 35332.0,
      "text": "The surge was terrible."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35356.0,
      "end_time": 37546.0,
      "text": "You had to have your camera rig tight in"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37570.0,
      "end_time": 38722.0,
      "text": "and your arm out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 38746.0,
      "end_time": 41104.0,
      "text": "because the surge kept throwing you into the rocks"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 41128.0,
      "end_time": 43748.0,
      "text": "while you&#39;re scanning up for that beautiful photograph."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 43772.0,
      "end_time": 46302.0,
      "text": "It was going OK, until ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 46326.0,
      "end_time": 47891.0,
      "text": "not OK."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 47915.0,
      "end_time": 51160.0,
      "text": "Something was terribly, terribly wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 51552.0,
      "end_time": 53388.0,
      "text": "I pulled my hand back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 53412.0,
      "end_time": 56540.0,
      "text": "and I had long, black sea urchin spines"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 56780.0,
      "end_time": 57678.0,
      "text": "all the way through my gloves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 57702.0,
      "end_time": 59801.0,
      "text": "which meant all the way through my hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 60344.0,
      "end_time": 62356.0,
      "text": "Now, this is bad."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 62380.0,
      "end_time": 65865.0,
      "text": "I mean, obviously when you have something all the way through your hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 65889.0,
      "end_time": 67103.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s kind of bad anyway,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 67127.0,
      "end_time": 71306.0,
      "text": "but in this case, sea urchins have a venom on them that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 71331.0,
      "end_time": 72924.0,
      "text": "if you&#39;ve ever tangled with them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 72948.0,
      "end_time": 77595.0,
      "text": "you know that a sea urchin spine in you gives you horrible, painful inflammation."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 77619.0,
      "end_time": 80316.0,
      "text": "But that wasn&#39;t even topmost in my mind at this point."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 80340.0,
      "end_time": 82491.0,
      "text": "This did not look real."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 82515.0,
      "end_time": 84979.0,
      "text": "I could not believe that this was my hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 85300.0,
      "end_time": 89762.0,
      "text": "Now, in a crisis, I tend to disassociate into, like, little scientists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 89786.0,
      "end_time": 92903.0,
      "text": "and I start talking very analytically."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 92927.0,
      "end_time": 95906.0,
      "text": "All analysis was gone, adrenaline brain kicked in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 95930.0,
      "end_time": 98769.0,
      "text": "and I just yanked the spines out."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 98793.0,
      "end_time": 100932.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t remember doing it."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 101665.0,
      "end_time": 105522.0,
      "text": "I just remember thinking, \"I can&#39;t get my glove off with these in here.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 105546.0,
      "end_time": 107642.0,
      "text": "I do remember taking the glove off"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 107666.0,
      "end_time": 111320.0,
      "text": "and a big plume of black coming up in front of my face."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 111875.0,
      "end_time": 116303.0,
      "text": "And biologist brain now shows up and starts freaking out."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 116327.0,
      "end_time": 119496.0,
      "text": "\"How could all that toxin have gotten into that wound already?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 119520.0,
      "end_time": 123640.0,
      "text": "Well, physicist brain then shows up and very calmly explains,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 123665.0,
      "end_time": 125363.0,
      "text": "\"No, no, no, we&#39;re at 50 feet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 125387.0,
      "end_time": 126864.0,
      "text": "red wavelengths are attenuated."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 126888.0,
      "end_time": 128819.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s blood -- not black."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 130566.0,
      "end_time": 131954.0,
      "text": "And sharks."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 132793.0,
      "end_time": 134392.0,
      "text": "So what are you gonna do?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 134965.0,
      "end_time": 139531.0,
      "text": "Well, I cranked my cummerbund down really hard over my hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 139555.0,
      "end_time": 142308.0,
      "text": "and I simply swam away."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 143780.0,
      "end_time": 148392.0,
      "text": "\"Let&#39;s let that big old cloud of blood dissipate a bit before we have to surface"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 148416.0,
      "end_time": 150224.0,
      "text": "through all of these sharks.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 150248.0,
      "end_time": 151715.0,
      "text": "So when I did surface,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 151739.0,
      "end_time": 153640.0,
      "text": "my warm-blooded-mammal brain"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 153664.0,
      "end_time": 155715.0,
      "text": "was in an absolute gibbering panic:"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 155740.0,
      "end_time": 159868.0,
      "text": "\"They don&#39;t feed when they&#39;re schooling. They don&#39;t feed when they&#39;re schooling."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 159892.0,
      "end_time": 161219.0,
      "text": "All the way up.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 161243.0,
      "end_time": 162427.0,
      "text": "And they didn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 162451.0,
      "end_time": 165667.0,
      "text": "So apparently, they have read the same books that I have."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 165691.0,
      "end_time": 167830.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 167107.0,
      "end_time": 168535.0,
      "text": "Now, it turns out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 168559.0,
      "end_time": 170871.0,
      "text": "when you&#39;ve been stabbed with sea urchin spines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 170895.0,
      "end_time": 173573.0,
      "text": "and you&#39;re two days away from any medical help,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 173597.0,
      "end_time": 177820.0,
      "text": "the thing that you&#39;ve got to do is, unfortunately, cook your hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 178621.0,
      "end_time": 181265.0,
      "text": "So you put it in water as hot as you can stand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 181289.0,
      "end_time": 182923.0,
      "text": "and you keep adding boiling water"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 182948.0,
      "end_time": 186262.0,
      "text": "until you think you will go absolutely insane."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 186286.0,
      "end_time": 187697.0,
      "text": "Now, it worked --"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 188249.0,
      "end_time": 192386.0,
      "text": "the hand itself did not work so well for several weeks after that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 192410.0,
      "end_time": 195548.0,
      "text": "but eventually, fine motor skills returned."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 195572.0,
      "end_time": 200166.0,
      "text": "All except for one spot, that stayed stiff and painful for weeks"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 200190.0,
      "end_time": 202392.0,
      "text": "after the other things had gotten better."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 202416.0,
      "end_time": 206660.0,
      "text": "So it turned out, I&#39;d broken off a tip of the urchin spine"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 206684.0,
      "end_time": 208787.0,
      "text": "in the joint itself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 208811.0,
      "end_time": 210761.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s why it wasn&#39;t getting better."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 210785.0,
      "end_time": 213744.0,
      "text": "So the orthopedist says, \"You know, we should get this out."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 213768.0,
      "end_time": 216414.0,
      "text": "Nothing too urgent, not an emergency.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 216438.0,
      "end_time": 219840.0,
      "text": "So we scheduled a small surgery for a few weeks out on a Monday."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 220476.0,
      "end_time": 222928.0,
      "text": "And on the Friday before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 222952.0,
      "end_time": 226200.0,
      "text": "I broke my pelvis in a horseback riding accident."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 226440.0,
      "end_time": 227743.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 227767.0,
      "end_time": 228976.0,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 229000.0,
      "end_time": 231611.0,
      "text": "So we kind of postponed that surgery."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 232461.0,
      "end_time": 237180.0,
      "text": "My broken pelvis and I were now facing six weeks on the couch,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 237420.0,
      "end_time": 242146.0,
      "text": "and I would have gone absolutely insane if it hadn&#39;t been for my friends."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 242170.0,
      "end_time": 245629.0,
      "text": "Spontaneous parties broke out at my house every night for weeks."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 245653.0,
      "end_time": 247929.0,
      "text": "I was fed. I was entertained."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 247953.0,
      "end_time": 249278.0,
      "text": "It was great."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 250150.0,
      "end_time": 253935.0,
      "text": "But that kind of enthusiasm is sort of hard to sustain over the long term,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 253960.0,
      "end_time": 257256.0,
      "text": "and eventually it petered down to just one friend,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 257279.0,
      "end_time": 259272.0,
      "text": "who would send me jokes during the day"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 259296.0,
      "end_time": 261899.0,
      "text": "and come and keep me company in the evenings --"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 261923.0,
      "end_time": 266289.0,
      "text": "someone I got to know a whole lot better during this period of convalescence."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 266314.0,
      "end_time": 268430.0,
      "text": "And when I was finally pronounced well enough"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 268454.0,
      "end_time": 270144.0,
      "text": "to do weight-bearing activities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 270168.0,
      "end_time": 273207.0,
      "text": "we loaded a telescope in the car and drove up into the mountains"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 273231.0,
      "end_time": 275347.0,
      "text": "to look at the Haleâ€“Bopp comet."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 275371.0,
      "end_time": 277465.0,
      "text": "Yes, we are geeks."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 277489.0,
      "end_time": 279188.0,
      "text": "And got caught in a landslide."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 279213.0,
      "end_time": 281158.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 281182.0,
      "end_time": 283446.0,
      "text": "I know -- like, really?"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 284510.0,
      "end_time": 285513.0,
      "text": "No. Just kidding."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 285537.0,
      "end_time": 286719.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 286743.0,
      "end_time": 289675.0,
      "text": "No more disasters. No. Just the opposite, in fact."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 289699.0,
      "end_time": 291239.0,
      "text": "That was 21 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 291263.0,
      "end_time": 293150.0,
      "text": "and for 19 of those years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 293174.0,
      "end_time": 296774.0,
      "text": "I have been married to that marvelous introvert"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 296798.0,
      "end_time": 299310.0,
      "text": "who never in a million years would have approached me"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 299334.0,
      "end_time": 301250.0,
      "text": "under other circumstances."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 301490.0,
      "end_time": 303109.0,
      "text": "We have a wonderful 14-year-old daughter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 303133.0,
      "end_time": 304740.0,
      "text": "who did all my illustrations."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 304764.0,
      "end_time": 306340.0,
      "text": "(Cheers and applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 306364.0,
      "end_time": 307525.0,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 307550.0,
      "end_time": 308888.0,
      "text": "So, pro tip:"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 308912.0,
      "end_time": 311695.0,
      "text": "apparently, nothing makes you sexier than needing a walker"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 311720.0,
      "end_time": 312955.0,
      "text": "on your first date."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 313393.0,
      "end_time": 316600.0,
      "text": "So this isn&#39;t a story about piercings"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 316300.0,
      "end_time": 318815.0,
      "text": "or sharks or boilings or breakings."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 318839.0,
      "end_time": 320273.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a love story."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 320758.0,
      "end_time": 323645.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a love story with a funny little epilogue."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 324845.0,
      "end_time": 328875.0,
      "text": "Now I was weight-bearing again, I could reschedule that surgery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 328899.0,
      "end_time": 330195.0,
      "text": "get the spine out."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 330219.0,
      "end_time": 331756.0,
      "text": "But I didn&#39;t need it anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 332407.0,
      "end_time": 334107.0,
      "text": "Turns out, when you break a bone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 334131.0,
      "end_time": 338560.0,
      "text": "your body scavenges calcium from all the bones in your body --"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 338810.0,
      "end_time": 341970.0,
      "text": "and from the little sea urchin spine that you happen to have lodged"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 341994.0,
      "end_time": 343998.0,
      "text": "in the joint of your finger."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 344220.0,
      "end_time": 345284.0,
      "text": "So yes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 346940.0,
      "end_time": 349482.0,
      "text": "my pelvis is now part sea urchin."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 349506.0,
      "end_time": 351330.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 351355.0,
      "end_time": 354445.0,
      "text": "So to biology brain, physicist brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 354469.0,
      "end_time": 356616.0,
      "text": "adrenaline brain, warm-blooded-mammal brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 356640.0,
      "end_time": 358647.0,
      "text": "I get to add \"urchin brain,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 358672.0,
      "end_time": 361974.0,
      "text": "with all of the superpowers that that confers."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 362393.0,
      "end_time": 363929.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t need to worry, though:"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 363953.0,
      "end_time": 366111.0,
      "text": "that I am not fully human is one of the things"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 366136.0,
      "end_time": 368129.0,
      "text": "that my family loves the most about me."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 368153.0,
      "end_time": 369240.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 369264.0,
      "end_time": 370459.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
